data.description: NORTHWESTERN SCHOOLS!! Here you go, UNIQUE property overlooking Green Acres Golf Course. Home features 4 bedrooms , 2 of those are master bedrooms with full baths in each. There is also a half bath located on main floor that has been updated . A walk out basement and a very large deck area for awesome summer get togethers. All appliances will remain with the property, as well as newer furnace and central air within the past 3 years added. Property is being sold in AS-IS condition and under assessed value.
